text: Phintella lunda is a jumping spider species in the genus Phintella that lives in Angola and was first described by Wanda Wesołowska in 2010. ==References== Category:Salticidae Category:Invertebrates of Angola Category:Spiders of Africa Category:Spiders described in 2010 Category:Taxa named by Wanda Wesołowska
title: Phintella lunda
